drop table 표준화정의서;

/*표준화정의서*/
create table 표준화정의서(
일련번호                NUMBER(10) NOT NULL,
테이블영문명            VARCHAR2(50) ,
테이블한글명            VARCHAR2(50) ,
순번                    NUMBER(10) ,
컬럼영문명              VARCHAR2(50) ,
컬럼한글명              VARCHAR2(50) ,
도메인                  VARCHAR2(50) ,
도메인DATATYPE          VARCHAR2(10) ,
타입                    VARCHAR2(10) ,
길이                    VARCHAR2(50) ,
PK여부                  VARCHAR2(10) ,
표_테이블영문명         VARCHAR2(50) ,
표_테이블한글명         VARCHAR2(50) ,
표_순번                 NUMBER(10) ,
표_컬럼영문명           VARCHAR2(50) ,
표_컬럼한글명           VARCHAR2(100) ,
표_도메인               VARCHAR2(50) ,
표_도메인DATA_TYPE      VARCHAR2(50) ,
표_타입                 VARCHAR2(50) ,
표_길이                 VARCHAR2(50) ,
표_PK여부               VARCHAR2(10) ,
사용유무                VARCHAR2(10) ,
NOTNULL                 VARCHAR2(10) ,
UNIQUE_YN               VARCHAR2(10) ,
사용여부                VARCHAR2(10) ,
비고                    VARCHAR2(1000) ,
변환규칙                VARCHAR2(1000) ,
이행SQL문               VARCHAR2(100) ,
이행전                  VARCHAR2(100) ,
이행전금액              VARCHAR2(100) ,
주제영역                VARCHAR2(50) ,
이행여부                VARCHAR2(10) ,
업무공통담당팀          VARCHAR2(50) ,
이행순번                VARCHAR2(50) ,
테스트시작삭제여부      VARCHAR2(10) ,
신규여부                VARCHAR2(10) ,
생성일시                VARCHAR2(50)
);
ALTER TABLE 표준화정의서 ADD CONSTRAINT pk_표준화정의서 PRIMARY KEY (일련번호);

GRANT SELECT, INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE ON 표준화정의서 TO py0777;

  FROM (
SELECT SUM(A.INSUR_PER) CNT
  FROM BANCA3.TCMPYIN A,
       BANCA3.TCMENLI B
 WHERE A.PRODT_COD = B.PRODT_COD(+)
   AND A.MAIN_PRDCOD = B.MAIN_PRDCOD(+)
   AND A.COOPE_INSCOD = B.COOPE_INSCOD(+)
   AND A.WOORI_COD = B.WOORI_COD(+)
   AND (A.COOPE_INSCOD, A.PRODT_COD) NOT IN ( SELECT  ''L01'' COOPE_INSCOD, ''5140037'' PRODT_COD FROM DUAL
                                              UNION ALL
                                              SELECT  ''L04'' COOPE_INSCOD, ''7466'' PRODT_COD FROM DUAL )
   AND (A.COOPE_INSCOD, A.PRODT_COD) NOT IN ( SELECT COOPE_INSCOD, PRODT_COD
                                                FROM LPETPDT )
       ) A,
       (
SELECT SUM(INSU_TM_CN) CNT
  FROM LPINSUM@MNBKSSDB B
 WHERE ( B.AFCO_CD_NO, B.PRD_CD_NO) IN ( SELECT COOPE_INSCOD, PRODT_COD 
                                           FROM LPETPDT )
   AND NOT EXISTS ( SELECT ''N'' 
                      FROM LPINSUM A
                     WHERE A.CIG_CD_NO            = B.CIG_CD_NO
                       AND A.AFCO_CD_NO           = B.AFCO_CD_NO
                       AND A.PRD_CD_NO            = B.PRD_CD_NO
                       AND A.INSU_TM_CN           = B.INSU_TM_CN
                       AND A.ILST_PI_TM_CN        = B.ILST_PI_TM_CN
                       AND A.SEX_NO               = B.SEX_NO
                       AND A.INSU_TM_YORAG_DIS_NO = B.INSU_TM_YORAG_DIS_NO
                       AND A.PI_TM_YORAG_DIS_NO   = B.PI_TM_YORAG_DIS_NO
                       AND A.ENT_MIN_AGE          = B.ENT_MIN_AGE
                       AND A.ENT_MAX_AGE          = B.ENT_MAX_AGE
                       AND A.PENS_STA_AGE         = B.PENS_STA_AGE
                       AND A.ULI_ILST_DIS_NO      = B.ULI_ILST_DIS_NO)
        ) B;','생명보험','L','','4067','','','');

select a.COOPE_INSCOD
     , a.DESGN_NO
     , a.BANK_POLNO
     , a.POLNO
     , a.SUBSC_NUM
     , a.PRODT_COD
     , a.CONTR_DTE
     , a','SELECT ''TNBCONT'','''', SYSDATE,'''', COUNT(*),''''
FROM (
     select a.COOPE_INSCOD, a.DESGN_NO, a.BANK_POLNO, a.POLNO
       from (
             select a.COOPE_INSCOD
                 , '''' as DESGN_NO
                 , a.BANK_POLNO
                 , case when a.POLNO     like ''NL%'' and a.BANK_POLNO is null then  a.POLNO
                        when a.POLNO not like ''NL%'' and a.BANK_POLNO is null then  a.POLNO
                        else a.BANK_POLNO
                     end as BK_MNG_NO
                 , a.POLNO
               from banca3.TNBCONT a
                  , banca3.TPIPROD b
                  , banca3.TQMCONT c
                  , banca3.TPLBSCI d
              where a.WOORI_COD    = b.WOORI_COD   (+)
                and a.COOPE_INSCOD = b.COOPE_INSCOD(+)
                and a.PRODT_COD    = b.PRODT_COD   (+)
                and a.COOPE_INSCOD = c.COOPE_INSCOD(+)
                and a.BANK_POLNO   = c.DESGN_NO    (+)
                and a.COOPE_INSCOD = d.COOPE_INSCOD(+)
                and a.POLNO        = d.POLNO       (+)
            ) a
          , (select a.COOPE_INSCOD
                  , case when a.POLNO     like ''NL%'' and a.BANK_POLNO is null then  a.POLNO
                         when a.POLNO not like ''NL%'' and a.BANK_POLNO is null then  a.POLNO
                         else a.BANK_POLNO
                    end as BK_MNG_NO
                  , max(a.CRDTE) as CRDTE
               from BANCA3.TNBCONT a
              group
                 by a.COOPE_INSCOD
                  , case when a.POLNO     like ''NL%'' and a.BANK_POLNO is null then  a.POLNO
                         when a.POLNO not like ''NL%'' and a.BANK_POLNO is null then  a.POLNO
                         else a.BANK_POLNO
                    end
             having count(1) >  1
            ) b
            , (select a.COOPE_INSCOD
                    , a.POLNO
                    , decode(a.USE_FLG, ''1'', ''Y'', ''N'') as USE_YN
                 from BANCA3.TCMSCRT a
                where a.SEQ_NO = (select max(SEQ_NO)
                                    from BANCA3.TCMSCRT
                                   where COOPE_INSCOD = a.COOPE_INSCOD
                                     and POLNO        = a.POLNO
                                 )
          ) c
      where a.COOPE_INSCOD = b.COOPE_INSCOD(+)
        and a.BK_MNG_NO    = b.BK_MNG_NO   (+)
        and a.COOPE_INSCOD = c.COOPE_INSCOD(+)
        and a.POLNO        = c.POLNO   (+)
     UNION ALL
     select a.COOPE_INSCOD, a.DESGN_NO, a.BANK_POLNO, '''' as POLNO
       from banca3.TQMCONT a
     , banca3.TPIPROD b 
     , banca3.TQLBSCI c
 where a.WOORI_COD    = b.WOORI_COD   (+)
   and a.COOPE_INSCOD = b.COOPE_INSCOD(+)
   and a.PRODT_COD    = b.PRODT_COD   (+)
   and a.COOPE_INSCOD = c.COOPE_INSCOD(+)
   and a.DESGN_NO     = c.DESGN_NO    (+)
       );','','손해보험','M','','1101','','신규','');

    from BANCA3.TQMRTPL a
     , BANCA3.TQMCONT b
 where a.COOPE_INSCOD = b.COOPE_INSCOD
   and a.DESGN_NO     = b.DESGN_NO
UNION ALL

     , BANCA3.TPIPROD c

     , a.CHAGE_NUM

     , a.RGTPL_TYP

           and a.DESGN_NO     = b.DESGN_NO
         UNION ALL
         select a.COOPE_INSCOD
              , case when b.POLNO is null then a.POLNO
                     when b.POLNO     like ''NL%'' and b.BANK_POLNO is null then  b.POLNO
                     when b.POLNO not like ''NL%'' and b.BANK_POLNO is null then  b.POLNO
                     else b.BANK_POLNO
                end as BK_MNG_NO
              , a.CHAGE_NUM
              , a.MRTGG_COD
          from BANCA3.TNBRTPL a
             , BANCA3.TNBCONT b
             , BANCA3.TPIPROD c
         where a.COOPE_INSCOD = b.COOPE_INSCOD
           and a.POLNO        = b.POLNO
           and b.WOORI_COD    = c.WOORI_COD
           and b.COOPE_INSCOD = c.COOPE_INSCOD

select a.COOPE_INSCOD
     , a.DESGN_NO
     , a.INPRD_TP_VAL
     , a.PMPRD_TP_VAL
     , a.INPRD_TP
     , a.PMPRD_TP
     , a.PMPRD_JONG
','SELECT ''TQLBSCI'','''', SYSDATE,'''', COUNT(*),''''
  FROM (
        select a.COOPE_INSCOD
             , a.DESGN_NO
             , TO_NUMBER(NVL(a.INPRD_TP_VAL,0))
             , TO_NUMBER(NVL(a.PMPRD_TP_VAL,0))
          from BANCA3.TQLBSCI a
             , BANCA3.TQMCONT b
         where a.COOPE_INSCOD = b.COOPE_INSCOD
           and a.DESGN_NO     = b.DESGN_NO
           and b.STATU_COD   != ''00''
        UNION ALL
        select a.COOPE_INSCOD
             , case when b.POLNO is null then a.POLNO
                    when b.POLNO     like ''NL%'' and b.BANK_POLNO is null then  b.POLNO      
                    when b.POLNO not like ''NL%'' and b.BANK_POLNO is null then  b.POLNO    
                    else b.BANK_POLNO
               end as BK_MNG_NO
             , TO_NUMBER(NVL(a.INPRD_TP_VAL,0))
             , TO_NUMBER(NVL(a.PMPRD_TP_VAL,0))
          from BANCA3.TPLBSCI a
             , BANCA3.TNBCONT b
             , BANCA3.TPIPROD c
         where a.COOPE_INSCOD = b.COOPE_INSCOD
           and a.POLNO        = b.POLNO
           and b.WOORI_COD    = c.WOORI_COD
           and b.COOPE_INSCOD = c.COOPE_INSCOD
           and b.PRODT_COD    = c.PRODT_COD
           and c.TYPE_COD     = ''1''
           and b.STATU_COD   != ''00''

     , BANCA3.TNBCONT b
     , BANCA3.TPIPROD c

   and a.POLNO        = b.POLNO

   and b.COOPE_INSCOD = c.COOPE_INSCOD

   and c.TYPE_COD     = ''1''
